On that fateful day....
I was walking in the snow toward 
Zol's pub when I saw a shadowy 
figure. It walked closer to me and 
I noted that it was a vampire. I 
pulled my sword out and quickly 
thrust at it and when I did the 
vampire disappeared and 
reappeared behind me and 
whispered in my ear 
"your destiny starts here..."
and bit me. It felt as if all my 
feelings and strength just burst 
out of me at the same time. All 
went black....and when I woke I 
was dazed looking around and I 
saw that the vampire was a 
female, she said hello and 
welcome to the family, 
I'm Shanki.
